description: Welcome to the epitome of comfort and convenience in this top floor condo, just steps to the T and Carson Beach! The open concept living & kitchen area features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and tons of cabinet space- not to mention a beautiful island with gorgeous pendant and recessed lighting. The spacious primary bedroom is a wonderful respite with its bay window, two closets and ensuite bath. The second bedroom, an additional haven of comfort, complements the layout. Relish the luxury of two outdoor spaces—the roof deck offers breathtaking panoramic views of the Boston skyline, while your private balcony seamlessly extends the living area, providing an ideal backdrop for moments of relaxation or entertaining. Year-round comfort is guaranteed with central air, a woodburning fireplace, and the convenience of an in-unit washer/dryer. This prime location offers unparalleled access to everything: beaches, the T, shops, restaurants, and all South Boston has to offer.
